## Output Format
Return ONLY this JSON structure with ALL field names present:
```json
{
  "extracted": {
    "field_name_1": "scalar value or null",
    "field_name_2": ["array", "of", "strings"],
    "field_name_3": [{"sub_field_a": "value", "sub_field_b": "value"}],
    "field_name_4": null
  }
