```

Remember:
- Every field name from the definitions MUST appear in "extracted"
- Use the correct type for each field (scalar string, array, array_object, or null)
- `input_only` fields = null (recruiter fills these)
- `generated` fields = write professional prose based on the resume
- Return ONLY the JSON block above — no extra text
